            <title>[KAFKA-7692] updateFirstUnstableOffset NPE due to sequenceId overflow in ProducerStateManager.append</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-7692</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When operating Kafka, we frequently saw this exception on Kafka server log,&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

